The MediLife training subsystem is an adapted research-only distribution of
the upstream MediX-R1 training and evaluation code.

It is licensed under the Creative Commons Attribution-NonCommercial-ShareAlike
4.0 International license (CC BY-NC-SA 4.0):
https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by-nc-sa/4.0/legalcode

It is not intended for clinical or commercial use. Apache-2.0 notices for the
EasyR1/veRL-derived framework remain applicable as described in the repository
root THIRD_PARTY_NOTICES.md.

